{"info": {"author": "jadbin", "author_email": "jadbin.com@hotmail.com", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: Apache Software License", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6", "Topic :: Internet :: WWW/HTTP", "Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Application Frameworks"], "description": "=======\ngspider\n=======\n\n.. image:: https://travis-ci.org/jadbin/gspider.svg?branch=master\n    :target: https://travis-ci.org/jadbin/gspider\n\n.. image:: https://coveralls.io/repos/jadbin/gspider/badge.svg?branch=master\n    :target: https://coveralls.io/github/jadbin/gspider?branch=master\n\n.. image:: https://img.shields.io/badge/license-Apache 2-blue.svg\n    :target: https://github.com/jadbin/gspider/blob/master/LICENSE\n\n\nA web spider framework based on `gevent`_ and `requests`_.\n\n\nSpider Example\n==============\n\n\u4ee5\u4e0b\u662f\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u4e00\u4e2a\u722c\u866b\u7c7b\u793a\u4f8b\uff0c\u5176\u4f5c\u7528\u4e3a\u722c\u53d6 `\u767e\u5ea6\u65b0\u95fb <http://news.baidu.com/>`_ \u7684\u70ed\u70b9\u8981\u95fb:\n\n.. code-block:: python\n\n    from gspider import Spider, HttpRequest, run_spider, Selector\n\n\n    class BaiduNewsSpider(Spider):\n        def start_requests(self):\n            yield HttpRequest(\"http://news.baidu.com/\")\n\n        def parse(self, response):\n            selector = Selector(response.text)\n            hot = selector.css(\"div.hotnews a\").text\n            self.log(\"Hot News:\")\n            for i in range(len(hot)):\n                self.log(\"%s: %s\", i + 1, hot[i])\n\n\n    if __name__ == '__main__':\n        run_spider(BaiduNewsSpider)\n\n\n\u5728\u722c\u866b\u7c7b\u4e2d\u6211\u4eec\u5b9a\u4e49\u4e86\u4e00\u4e9b\u65b9\u6cd5\uff1a\n\n- ``start_requests``: \u8fd4\u56de\u722c\u866b\u521d\u59cb\u8bf7\u6c42\u3002\n- ``parse``: \u5904\u7406\u8bf7\u6c42\u5f97\u5230\u7684\u9875\u9762\uff0c\u8fd9\u91cc\u501f\u52a9 ``Selector`` \u53caCSS Selector\u8bed\u6cd5\u63d0\u53d6\u5230\u4e86\u6211\u4eec\u6240\u9700\u7684\u6570\u636e\u3002\n\n\nDocumentation\n=============\n\nhttp://gspider.readthedocs.io/\n\n\n.. _gevent: https://pypi.org/project/gevent\n.. _requests: https://pypi.org/project/requests\n", "description_content_type": "", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/jadbin/gspider", "keywords": "", "license": "Apache 2", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "gspider", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/gspider/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/gspider/", "project_urls": {"Homepage": "https://github.com/jadbin/gspider"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/gspider/0.1.1/", "requires_dist": null, "requires_python": "", "summary": "A web spider framework based on gevent and requests", "version": "0.1.1", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/jadbin/gspider\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"https://travis-ci.org/jadbin/gspider.svg?branch=master\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/71e0f284960fed9be8524e6de5d3049751085354/68747470733a2f2f7472617669732d63692e6f72672f6a616462696e2f677370696465722e7376673f6272616e63683d6d6173746572\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://coveralls.io/github/jadbin/gspider?branch=master\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"https://coveralls.io/repos/jadbin/gspider/badge.svg?branch=master\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/6a360f7703557f58453e37a66182e681edfcb7fa/68747470733a2f2f636f766572616c6c732e696f2f7265706f732f6a616462696e2f677370696465722f62616467652e7376673f6272616e63683d6d6173746572\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/jadbin/gspider/blob/master/LICENSE\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/license-Apache2-blue.svg\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/97b204f8a706ba1b42c9be4acbf7ad352fdae111/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f62616467652f6c6963656e73652d417061636865322d626c75652e737667\"></a>\n<p>A web spider framework based on <a href=\"https://pypi.org/project/gevent\" rel=\"nofollow\">gevent</a> and <a href=\"https://pypi.org/project/requests\" rel=\"nofollow\">requests</a>.</p>\n<div id=\"spider-example\">\n<h2>Spider Example</h2>\n<p>\u4ee5\u4e0b\u662f\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u4e00\u4e2a\u722c\u866b\u7c7b\u793a\u4f8b\uff0c\u5176\u4f5c\u7528\u4e3a\u722c\u53d6 <a href=\"http://news.baidu.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">\u767e\u5ea6\u65b0\u95fb</a> \u7684\u70ed\u70b9\u8981\u95fb:</p>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">gspider</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Spider</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">HttpRequest</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">run_spider</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Selector</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"k\">class</span> <span class=\"nc\">BaiduNewsSpider</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Spider</span><span class=\"p\">):</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">def</span> <span class=\"nf\">start_requests</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"p\">):</span>\n        <span class=\"k\">yield</span> <span class=\"n\">HttpRequest</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"http://news.baidu.com/\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n    <span class=\"k\">def</span> <span class=\"nf\">parse</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">response</span><span class=\"p\">):</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">selector</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">Selector</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">response</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">text</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">hot</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">selector</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">css</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"div.hotnews a\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">text</span>\n        <span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">log</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"Hot News:\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"k\">for</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"ow\">in</span> <span class=\"nb\">range</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">len</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hot</span><span class=\"p\">)):</span>\n            <span class=\"bp\">self</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">log</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"si\">%s</span><span class=\"s2\">: </span><span class=\"si\">%s</span><span class=\"s2\">\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"o\">+</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">hot</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"p\">])</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"vm\">__name__</span> <span class=\"o\">==</span> <span class=\"s1\">'__main__'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">run_spider</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">BaiduNewsSpider</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n<p>\u5728\u722c\u866b\u7c7b\u4e2d\u6211\u4eec\u5b9a\u4e49\u4e86\u4e00\u4e9b\u65b9\u6cd5\uff1a</p>\n<ul>\n<li><tt>start_requests</tt>: \u8fd4\u56de\u722c\u866b\u521d\u59cb\u8bf7\u6c42\u3002</li>\n<li><tt>parse</tt>: \u5904\u7406\u8bf7\u6c42\u5f97\u5230\u7684\u9875\u9762\uff0c\u8fd9\u91cc\u501f\u52a9 <tt>Selector</tt> \u53caCSS Selector\u8bed\u6cd5\u63d0\u53d6\u5230\u4e86\u6211\u4eec\u6240\u9700\u7684\u6570\u636e\u3002</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div id=\"documentation\">\n<h2>Documentation</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://gspider.readthedocs.io/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://gspider.readthedocs.io/</a></p>\n</div>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 6925825, "releases": {"0.1.0": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "7981c01a07b11474f9b14f5b2dc1e454", "sha256": "1b09f1e4389f0fad7c866036baa9ab3d9987e1cdbbc9f9b8f7f8f27c45555325"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "gspider-0.1.0.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "7981c01a07b11474f9b14f5b2dc1e454", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 23416, "upload_time": "2020-03-20T06:56:44", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-03-20T06:56:44.007004Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/f0/30/6556cb25d075e23ec2ff41df90088c040decd752cc2a76b8080ef9f994bd/gspider-0.1.0.tar.gz", "yanked": false}], "0.1.1": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "472bdf84acfcd8b5084ee00477738157", "sha256": "da0be69cf6759a404e3b0d79acac52615113776ac550a3dbc0a1b6f13fb901eb"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "gspider-0.1.1.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "472bdf84acfcd8b5084ee00477738157", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 26472, "upload_time": "2020-04-01T07:36:54", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-04-01T07:36:54.816973Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/ab/fe/5d13fbd53689938baafdeabc2f0f4c6eca2ed1714a54dc82d0158beaf9d6/gspider-0.1.1.tar.gz", "yanked": false}]}, "urls": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "472bdf84acfcd8b5084ee00477738157", "sha256": "da0be69cf6759a404e3b0d79acac52615113776ac550a3dbc0a1b6f13fb901eb"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "gspider-0.1.1.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "472bdf84acfcd8b5084ee00477738157", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 26472, "upload_time": "2020-04-01T07:36:54", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-04-01T07:36:54.816973Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/ab/fe/5d13fbd53689938baafdeabc2f0f4c6eca2ed1714a54dc82d0158beaf9d